title: 06/18/21 DPS Hour 1 Alex Schiffer
itunes:title: 06/18/21 DPS Hour 1 Alex Schiffer
description:
Doug Gottlieb and Jason McIntyre, in for Dan Patrick, react to the Bucks forcing Game 7 with the Nets. The guys debate Ty Lue's success with the Clippers. Nets beat writer for The Athletic Alex Schiffer joins the guys to give the latest on the status of James Harden and Kyrie Irving. Doug and Jason debate Kyrie's playoff legacy. Plus, is Aaron Rodgers being selfish?
